<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1176.106517.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Photographs showing the A type locality of Amynthas sakonnakhonensis sp. nov. from Nong Tuet, Samakkee Pattana, Akat Amnuai, Sakon Nakhon, Thailand B living specimen under the stone near casts C coloration of a living paratype, and D coloration of a newly collected paratype (CUMZ 3824) after the first preservation step in 30 % (v / v) ethanol." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897720" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1176.106517.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. External and internal morphology of Amynthas sakonnakhonensis sp. nov., holotype (CUMZ 3823) A external ventral view B internal dorsal view, and C spermatheca with location of spermathecal pore arrowed." ;
